                        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8)),
                    child: Text(
                        l.partyPending <= 0
                            ? "SETTLED"
                            : l.isPaymentOverdue
                                ? "OVERDUE"
                                : l.isDueSoon
                                    ? "DUE SOON"
                                    : "OUTSTANDING",
